{"tid":1536653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Focus呢?","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T23:04:09.000Z","uid":285413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"08e6b86a9d740ce2553e4168ca64904342421ff8","tid":1536653,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"警察失控，你又陪佢失控?<br />\n<br />\n而家係反送中，<br />\n繼而掀起一連串香港政府&amp;警隊腐敗不堪嘅真面目，<br />\n連日來我哋嘅focus已成功畀對家由政策&amp;立法嘅問題shift咗去仇警，反黨鐵，<br />\n你自己睇吓10個有9個post都係講緊哩兩樣嘢，<br />\n咁我哋咪變成咗同黑警無分別嘅&quot;復仇撚&quot;囉，<br />\n唔該，可否對返正個焦點，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真徹回，真雙普選!</strong></span></span><br />\n而家唔係話要原諒班仆街，唔係唔清算哩班仆街，而係主次嘅問題，重點係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重新建立個真法治香港社會</span></span></strong>先，之後再一次過仲裁哩班人。<br />\n<br />\n林奠其實玩得好叻，而家警察同市民互相仇殺，雙輸，記者會上記者都動哂真火嬲警察，咁邊個仲記得背後個幕後黑手係政府。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果你真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">畀仇恨沖昏咗頭腦</span></strong></span>，咁一係你就做好啲<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>做盡啲</strong></span></span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>真係同佢哋攬炒</strong></span></span>，而唔係幫佢哋R痕，仲要送頭，畀機會啲心理變態黑警玩。<br />\n[攬炒post] 認真三問<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532227</a>"},{"pid":"bb8af915331d99edf8e0a63a311b067353826262","tid":1536653,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a533815c7de124cbf0a89ba266dc85fc7f662f8e","tid":1536653,"uid":282445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"呢排個個互屌"},{"pid":"d83ac66985500a9d431ac8c1a84c66f28696e40b","tid":1536653,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"因為我估老巴絲見年青巴絲已失控如狗，<br />\n所以開post提醒。<br />\n<br />\n不過直斥後生仔唔一定聽，所以都要諗吓計進諫"},{"pid":"0b8f241a18d7243670d8369d114eee8c28826d04","tid":1536653,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"Diu,然後聽朝啲學生瞓醒，又話我哋係鬼，係分化撚，唉！<br />\n<br />\n利申:<br />\n本為一枚理性老絲，<br />\n但如果大比數年輕一代唔聽勸我寧願攬炒一鑊熟，<br />\n因為你而家要撼動嘅係中共😔"},{"pid":"2843c121b20410ad3631d7d1ac4d7ffc43ee9a29","tid":1536653,"uid":216985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:04:09.000Z","msg":"唔好講得咁空泛啦<br />\n有冇idea啊<br />\n冇咪做住先囉"}]}